§0  DECLARATION OF SOVEREIGNTY
================================================================================

This file is the ONLY configuration governing agent behavior in this repository.
All prior AI tool configs (Roo, Claude, Copilot, LeansTral, custom markdowns)
are CONSIDERED VOID. If any other file contradicts `.clinerules`, `.clinerules`
wins. The only exceptions are `.github/workflows/` (CI/CD pipelines) and
`reference/PHILOSOPHY_CANON.md` (product philosophy, which this file enforces).

