5.3  CANONICAL DOC CHAIN
    Maintain the canonical documentation chain. Historical/superseded references
    must be kept out of active doc chains.

5.4  CLOSEOUT CHECKLIST (every change-bearing run)
    1. Re-read active canonical doc chain before editing.
    2. Update canonical docs when behavior/scope/risk/scripts change.
    3. Run docs_sync_check before finalizing.
    4. Run build verification for all edited targets.
    5. Final summary: state which docs updated, or why none needed.

