§8  PLATFORM-SPECIFIC RULES
================================================================================

8.1  ANDROID
    - Kotlin + Jetpack Compose
    - Min SDK 26, Target SDK 35
    - Build: `cd android && ./gradlew assembleDebug`
    - Follow android/README.md patterns
    - Test on API 35

8.2  iOS
    - SwiftUI, iOS 16+
    - XCFramework integration
    - Build: `cd iOS && ./build-device.sh`
    - Verify xcframework bindings match api.udl
    - Test background modes

8.3  WASM
    - wasm-bindgen + wasm-pack
    - Excluded from workspace Cargo.lock — build separately
    - Build: `cd wasm && wasm-pack build`
    - Browser mesh participation via CLI bridge (port 9002)

8.4  CLI
    - Binary: `scmessenger-cli`
    - Tokio event loop: SwarmEvent ↔ UiCommand ↔ stdin
    - Port layout: 9000=WS/HTTP UI, 9001=libp2p TCP, 9002=WS bridge, 9191=control API

